Upstream-Name: Northstar
Upstream-Contact: Andreas Røsdal <andreas.rosdal@gmail.com>
Source: https://github.com/nordstjernen-web/northstar-browser
Comment:
 Northstar is the open-source GPL edition of the Nordstjernen project.
 The browser engine is original C written from scratch — it is not a
 fork of Gecko, WebKit, or Blink.
 .
 The upstream tarball must include the meson subprojects (lexbor,
 quickjs-ng, wuffs, plmpeg) so the package builds without network
 access; see debian/README.source.

